title: DDFP 330: Best wide receivers & free agency fits
itunes:title: DDFP 330: Best wide receivers & free agency fits
description:
Shek is joined by Handsome Hank and Elliot Harrison to debate the best wide receivers in the NFL, where top free agents fit best and the best leading man in Hollywood. Plus, Michael Fabiano joins in for a very early look at the 2015 NFL Fantasy landscape. 

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
